{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://theora.ai/schemas/knowledge-base.json",
  "title": "Theora Knowledge Base",
  "description": "Dublin Core-aligned knowledge base definition for bulk import/export. Uses Dublin Core metadata standard for interoperability with library systems, digital repositories, and academic tools.",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["name", "items"],
  "properties": {
    "name": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Knowledge base name. Dublin Core: title"
    },
    "title": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Dublin Core: title - Alternative to 'name'"
    },
    "description": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Dublin Core: description - Knowledge base description"
    },
    "creator": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Dublin Core: creator - Who created this KB"
    },
    "date": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "date",
      "description": "Dublin Core: date - Creation date (ISO 8601)"
    },
    "language": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Dublin Core: language - Primary language (ISO 639)"
    },
    "publisher": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Dublin Core: publisher - Publishing organization"
    },
    "rights": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Dublin Core: rights - Access rights statement"
    },
    "source": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Dublin Core: source - Original source of this KB definition"
    },
    "subject": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": { "type": "string" },
      "description": "Dublin Core: subject - Topic keywords/tags"
    },
    "coverage": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Dublin Core: coverage - Spatial or temporal coverage"
    },
    "items": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 1,
      "items": { "$ref": "#/$defs/resourceItem" }
    }
  },
  "$defs": {
    "resourceItem": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["url", "title"],
      "properties": {
        "id": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Stable identifier for the item"
        },
        "url": {
          "type": "string",
          "format": "uri",
          "description": "Dublin Core: identifier - Resource URL"
        },
        "title": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Dublin Core: title - Resource title"
        },
        "description": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Dublin Core: description - Resource description"
        },
        "creator": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Dublin Core: creator - Author/creator"
        },
        "date": {
          "type": "string",
          "format": "date",
          "description": "Dublin Core: date - Publication date"
        },
        "language": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Dublin Core: language - Resource language"
        },
        "publisher": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Dublin Core: publisher - Publishing organization"
        },
        "rights": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Dublin Core: rights - Access rights"
        },
        "source": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Dublin Core: source - Original source"
        },
        "subject": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": { "type": "string" },
          "description": "Dublin Core: subject - Topic keywords"
        },
        "coverage": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Dublin Core: coverage - Spatial/temporal coverage"
        },
        "type": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Dublin Core: type - Resource type"
        },
        "format": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Dublin Core: format - Media format/MIME type"
        },
        "contributor": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Dublin Core: contributor - Contributing entity"
        },
        "relation": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": { "type": "string" },
          "description": "Dublin Core: relation - Related resources"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

## Why Dublin Core?

[Dublin Core](https://www.dublincore.org/) is a widely-used metadata standard for describing digital resources. Using it provides:

- **Interoperability**: Works with library systems, digital repositories, academic tools
- **Familiarity**: Researchers and librarians already know these fields
- **Standards compliance**: Aligns with best practices for metadata
- **Tooling**: Existing validators, converters, and integrations

